		}
		{
			description: ["The Primitive Blast Furnace converts Iron and Charcoal into Steel without electricity — a crucial material for building the steam-powered machines that follow. Construct the structure from Firebricks, then feed it charcoal and iron. Steel unlocks the first generation of GregTech machinery."]
