		}
		{
			description: ["The Low-Pressure Steam Boiler converts water and solid fuel into Steam — the power medium for GregTech's first generation of machines. Connect it to a Steam Machine Hull with pipes and feed it water continuously. Without steam, no early GregTech machine will run."]
